OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1784667779
OL,3,CTrains cancelled and roads closed
OL,4,Cafter fire at railway station
OL,6,FTrains have been cancelled and roads
OL,7,Fclosed as firefighters from across
OL,8,FSouth Devon tackle a blaze at Paignton
OL,9,FRailway Station.
OL,11,FGreat Western Railway says signalling
OL,12,Fand infrastructure have been affected
OL,13,Fand it's unlikely trains will run
OL,14,Fbetween Paignton and Newton Abbot
OL,15,Ftoday.
OL,17,FMeanwhile, Torbay Road and Hyde Road
OL,18,Fhave been closed and emergency
OL,19,Fservices are on the scene.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/3
