OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1784667779
OL,3,CTrains cancelled and roads closed
OL,4,Cafter fire at railway station
OL,6,FDevon and Somerset Fire and Rescue
OL,7,FService says seven appliances are
OL,8,Fthere, along with crews from Paignton,
OL,9,FTorquay, Brixham, Newton Abbot, Totnes
OL,10,Fand Honiton.
OL,12,FGreat Western Railway said on its
OL,13,Fwebsite: "A fire has broken out at
OL,14,FPaignton Station, affecting signalling
OL,15,Fand surrounding infrastructure.
OL,16,FEmergency Services are on site, but is
OL,17,Fproving a long job, and due to the
OL,18,Fnature of the damage, it is unlikely
OL,19,Fthat we will be able to safely run
OL,20,Ftrains on this line today.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/3
