OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1784667779
OL,3,CTrains cancelled and roads closed
OL,4,Cafter fire at railway station
OL,6,F"No trains will run between Newton
OL,7,FAbbot and Paignton until further
OL,8,Fnotice. Train services from Exeter St
OL,9,FDavid's will all terminate at Newton
OL,10,FAbbot."
OL,12,FThis is a developing story - updates
OL,13,Fto follow.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/3
